    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1911-05-27T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1911-05-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="737"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d737">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President</gloss> to Provisional
                        President <persName type="to">de la Barra</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">The White House</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-05-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 27, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I extend to your excellency my hearty congratulations upon your elevation to the
                    Chief Magistracy of the Republic of Mexico, confident that your conduct of the
                    high office, will conduce to the peace and welfare of Mexico and to the
                    happiness and prosperity of the Mexican people.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Wm. H. Taft.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
